Class FlowProgrammerService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.protocol_plugin.openflow.internal.FlowProgrammerService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandProvider, IMessageListener, IInventoryShimExternalListener, IInventoryShimInternalListener, IContainerAware, IContainerListener, IPluginInFlowProgrammerService

    public class FlowProgrammerService
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPluginInFlowProgrammerService, IMessageListener, IContainerListener, IInventoryShimExternalListener, CommandProvider, IContainerAware
    Represents the openflow plugin component in charge of programming the flows the flow programming and relay them to functional modules above SAL.
